in&nbsp;\u2013 mixing\n* Chris Gehringer&nbsp;\u2013 mastering\n{{div col end}}\n\n== Charts ==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n=== Weekly charts ===\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2016)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|5|artist=Rihanna feat. Drake|song=Work|accessdate=March 5, 2016|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|14|artist=Rihanna feat. Drake|song=Work|accessdate=March 2, 2016|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|6|artist=Rihanna feat. Drake|song=Work|accessdate=March 5, 2016|rowheader=true|refname=Flanders}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Belgium ([[Ultratop]] Flanders Urban)<ref name=\"Flanders\"/>\n| 1\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia|1|artist=Rihanna feat. Drake|song=Work|accessdate=March 5, 2016|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Brazil ([[Billboard Brasil Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]])<ref name=bra>{{cite web|url=http://billboard.com.br/rankings |title=Hot 100 Billboard Brasil \u2013 weekly |work=[[Billboard Brasil]] |date=July 18, 2016 |accessdate=July 18, 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160716161516/http://billboard.com.br/rankings |archivedate=July 16, 2016 }}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n{{singlechart|Canada|1|artist=Rihanna|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 1, 2016}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Colombia ([[National-Report]])<ref name=\"Colombia\">{{cite web|title=National Report - Top Nacional|language=Spanish|url=http://national-report.com/externos/RYM-TopNacional.php|date=May 11, 2016|publisher=National Report|access-date=May 11, 2016|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150904025448/http://national-report.com/externos/RYM-TopNacional.php|archive-date=September 4, 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n| 4\n|-\n{{singlechart|Czechdigital|3|year=2016|week=09|accessdate=March 8, 2016|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Denmark|1|artist=Rihanna feat. Drake|song=Work|accessdate=March 2, 2016|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Dominican Republic ([[